  <body>
    <segment id="1">
Confusing</segment>
    <segment id="16" parent="17" relname="condition">

Anyone who wants to go from Wursthof to the market,</segment>
    <segment id="17" parent="19" relname="span"> 

must pay close attention.</segment>
    <segment id="2" parent="20" relname="span"> 

Parked cars up to the intersections obstruct the view.</segment>
    <segment id="3" parent="2" relname="result">  

Often, it is only in the middle of the street that you can see if you can turn.</segment>
    <segment id="4" parent="21" relname="list">  

Pedestrians and cyclists scurry around and should not be harmed.</segment>
    <segment id="5" parent="23" relname="joint">

It&apos;s a good thing that not all wishes are fulfilled.</segment>
    <segment id="6" parent="23" relname="joint">  

This is the case after the opening of the Wursthof in both directions, for example.</segment>
    <segment id="7" parent="28" relname="span">  

It is certainly a strange argument that the curbs should be twelve centimeters high for traffic in both directions,,</segment>
    <segment id="18" parent="7" relname="circumstance"> 

when in fact many streets don&apos;t have any at all.</segment>
    <segment id="8" parent="24" relname="span"> 

But in Mönchen and Zinnaer Straße, pedestrians do not step directly onto the road.</segment>
    <segment id="9" parent="8" relname="cause">  

First, they have to pass parked cars.</segment>
    <segment id="10" parent="25" relname="span">  

And the Mittelstraße is not so easily compared to the other streets.</segment>
    <segment id="11" parent="10" relname="evidence"> 

There is hardly any through traffic here.</segment>
    <segment id="12" parent="25" relname="interpretation"> 

This is likely a big difference compared to the other main arteries of the city.</segment>
    <segment id="13" parent="14" relname="concession">

The suggestion to examine whether a change of direction in the existing one-way streets leads to shorter routes is useful.</segment>
    <segment id="14" parent="27" relname="span">  

However, those who want to go from Lessingstraße to the city center would then have to take detours.</segment>
    <segment id="15" parent="31" relname="summary"> 

Not everyone will ever be satisfied.</segment>
<group id="19" type="span" parent="22" relname="span" />
